data.description: You have finally found your piece of paradise, away from the noise and chaos this move in ready home is nestled away on an oversized corner lot in the North end of the city. Featuring a den and additional seating area this home has all the space you need! The surrounding peace and serenity make this home an absolute dream escape. The home has had numerous upgrades which include the perfect chef's kitchen with new appliances and an air fryer convection oven. There is a Generac, whole home generator which runs of an independent 500 gallon propane tank, new water system and RO system, new flooring inside and decking outside. Working from home or for the avid gamer in the family the quantum fiber internet has speeds out of this world. The 12 camera security system also adds peace of mind This home has so much to offer and needs to be at the top of your to see list.
